For the last two weeks in a row my store has been #1.  why is this exciting??? its exciting cause we havn't been #1 in the last 13 periods.  my store right now is kicking some major ass, and it makes all the more exciting to go to work.  i know there are only going to be a handful of people that understand what the hell i am talking about.  oh by the way i have been running shifts for the last two weeks and every shift except one has been over sales and i have never not saved over at least a percent of labor.






thanks for reading 

mike

i have tomorrow and thursday off!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!  thats the first time in three months that i have had two days off in a week.  the sad part is that even with the two days off i will still probably work around 30-35 hours this week. saturday will suck i can't go to the okay bowl because i will be in a LAS meeting from 10-5.  o well shit happens.  lots of random things are going on right now in my life and i really havn't been able to make much sense of them.  i guess in time everything works its self out.  




later all

mike

i havn't had a real post in awhile so i think now is a great time for one. things are getting better.  my back dosn't hurt so much anymore, my leg does though but thats something that i think physical therapy can fix.  i have been working alot lately. and i think that i am doing something right cause my boss is trying to get me to become a manager.  i'm just not sure if i want the job or not cause that would mean i would work alot more and i would have atleast one closing shift which would probably be on sundays.  sundays suck cause were always slow especially now that football is over.  tonight we sent one of are drivers on a run and it took him an hour and forty-five minutes and he never even found the house.  the problem being that he was over by 19th street and the customer lives in chamber creek.  need less to say my boss was a little pissed off cause we all thought something bad had happened to him. so he is on probation now and my boss told him that if he ever leaves for a delivery again without a map book she would fire him.  this isn't the first time we have had a problem with getting lost. other then all this though life is going great.  my parents went to the home show a couple of weeks ago and decided to buy a hot tub so we will getting that sometime in the next couple of weeks.


i guess thats all for now


mike
YAYAYAYAYAYYAYAYAYAYAYAYYAYAY!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! I DONT HAVE TO WORK TOMORROW!!!!! I ACTUALLY GET TO HANG OUT WITH MY FRIENDS FOR THE FIRST TIME IN OVER A WEEK!!
tonight was one of the funnest nights that i have had in  a while

can't sleep at night anymore but i have no problem sleeping through all my classes today. went to the doc today i have that really bad feeling that when i see my other doc that i am not going to like what he has to tell me.  i dont have time for this.  it always seems to come at the worst times.  freshman year at the end of the summer so i couldn't play football.  football season again senior year the pain returns and again i go under the knife.  now i have school, work and about a thousand other things to do.  this time if i have to go under the knife again its going to really mess me up.  cause if you are ever lucky enough to have this done the third time they have to do it the fuse the disc.  which means i wouldn't be able to move for like to months and i would shrink a couple of inches.  its weird though cause the first two times i had it done i was never scared and now even though i not sure if i'm even going to have to have it done i actually am a little scared.  i guess i should also include that if it ends up that i just strained it a little that means that i have to start physical therapy again.  


thats all for now


mike
